Methodology:  Initial record of human interaction with SCP-3454 the Land of Tall Bees.

Test Results:  Subject directed to extend right arm through SCP-3454 the portal to the Land of Tall Bees. Exploration lasts three minutes, and subject returns unharmed.

Notes:  Subject was noted to exclaim,  upon exiting.6
